      "span_text": "Third, the  approach delivers estimates of the common component which are obtained (i) by detrending the data by estimating the slope of the trend with the mean of the data in first difference; then (ii) by estimating the factors in first differences; and, finally, (iii) by cumulating the differenced estimator to obtain an estimate of the levels."
